OL,3,CThree Southampton family members
OL,4,Cappear in court on weapons charges
OL,6,FThree family members have appeared in
OL,7,Fcourt in Southampton charged with
OL,8,Fmultiple weapons offences.
OL,10,FVickrum Digwa, 23, appeared at
OL,11,FSouthampton Magistrates' Court to face
OL,12,Fsix counts of possessing an offensive
OL,13,Fweapon in a private place.
OL,15,FThe alleged weapons are a flick knife,
OL,16,Fan extendable baton, knuckledusters, a
OL,17,Fmachete, swords and kusaris.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
