OL,3,CThree Southampton family members
OL,4,Cappear in court on weapons charges
OL,6,FHis father, Moga Singh, 52, and his
OL,7,Fbrother, Gurpreet Digwa, 27; both of
OL,8,FSt Denys Road, Southampton, Hampshire,
OL,9,Fappeared alongside him to face the
OL,10,Fsame charges while Gurpreet faced four
OL,11,Fadditional charges.
OL,13,FThey are charged with possessing an
OL,14,Foffensive weapon, an ASP, in a public
OL,15,Fplace, possessing a prohibited weapon,
OL,16,Fan air rifle, possessing an axe in a
OL,17,Fpublic place and possessing a knife, a
OL,18,Fkirpan, in a public place.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
