OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780441387
OL,3,CThree Southampton family members
OL,4,Cappear in court on weapons charges
OL,6,FNatalie Angel, prosecuting, asked the
OL,7,Fmagistrates for time for the
OL,8,Fprosecution to consider which charges
OL,9,Fagainst the three defendants to
OL,10,Fproceed with and told the court: "A
OL,11,Fnumber of weapons were recovered in
OL,12,Fthis case."
OL,14,FHarmail Gill, defending all three
OL,15,Ffamily members, asked for an
OL,16,Fadjournment of at least four weeks for
OL,17,Fboth sides to consider the charges.
OL,26,@rD@bOU
