PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780441387
OL,3,CThree Southampton family members
OL,4,Cappear in court on weapons charges
OL,6,FHe told the court this would allow
OL,7,Fthem to "be in a position where we are
OL,8,Fnot arriving on the day of court not
OL,9,Fknowing what charges the Crown are
OL,10,Fgoing ahead with".
OL,12,FJennifer Pitt, chair of the
OL,13,Fmagistrates, adjourned the proceedings
OL,14,Funtil a further hearing on July 9 and
OL,15,Freleased Moga Singh and Gurpreet Digwa
OL,16,Fon unconditional bail until then, and
OL,17,FVickrum Digwa on technical bail as he
OL,18,Fis serving a jail sentence.
OL,26,@oD@IOUrD@QO]
