OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780441387
OL,3,CThree Southampton family members
OL,4,Cappear in court on weapons charges
OL,6,FMs Pitt told the three defendants: "We
OL,7,Fhave been asked to adjourn matters and
OL,8,Fwe are prepared to do so as we think
OL,9,Fit is in the interests of justice to
OL,10,Flook at the charges and decide what
OL,11,Fexactly is going to go ahead or not so
OL,12,Fwe know what is going to happen at the
OL,13,Fnext date.
OL,15,F"We are adjourning matters until 9th
OL,16,FJuly at 2pm."
OL,26,@nD@dOUwD@AOUxD@MO]
